OL,3,CUK border chief to step down after
OL,4,Cfailure to reduce small boat crossings
OL,6,FThe UK's border chief - who was tasked
OL,7,Fwith decreasing the number of small
OL,8,Fboat crossings - will step down from
OL,9,Fhis role at the end of this month.
OL,11,FMartin Hewitt is due to step down at
OL,12,Fthe end of the month, home office
OL,13,Fsources have confirmed to ITV News.
OL,15,FIt comes after figures show the
OL,16,Fgovernment has failed to reduce small
OL,17,Fboats crossing the Channel - with more
OL,18,Fthan 40,000 crossings last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
