OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774026671
OL,3,CUK border chief to step down after
OL,4,Cfailure to reduce small boat crossings
OL,6,FHewitt took on the role in 2024 -
OL,7,Fafter a decades-long career in
OL,8,Fpolicing and crisis management.
OL,10,FOne home officer insider told The Sun
OL,11,FNewspaper that Hewitt will step down
OL,12,Famid a view that for "objectives were
OL,13,Fnot being met".
OL,15,F"There was a view that the objectives
OL,16,Fwere not being met, and there needed
OL,17,Fto be a tighter, more defined
OL,18,Foperational focus," the source told
OL,19,FThe Sun.
OL,26,@tD@VOUuD@NO]wD@AOU
