CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774026671
OL,3,CUK border chief to step down after
OL,4,Cfailure to reduce small boat crossings
OL,6,FHewitt has previously voiced concerns
OL,7,Fabout the lack of support from the
OL,8,FFrench authorities in reducing the
OL,9,Fnumber of crossings - hitting out at
OL,10,Fwhat he called "political instability".
OL,12,FIn October, he was asked by MPs about
OL,13,Fwhen a new tactic would come into
OL,14,Fforce which would allow French cops to
OL,15,Fintercept boats at sea - after
OL,16,Fpolitical discussions earlier in the
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
