OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"It is frustrating that it's taken the
OL,12,Ftime that it has," he told the home
OL,13,Faffairs select committee.
OL,15,F"Your point about the political
OL,16,Finstability, clearly that has been a
OL,17,Fbackdrop."
