OL,3,CUK border chief to step down after
OL,4,Cfailure to reduce small boat crossings
OL,6,FThe move comes as the prime minister
OL,7,Fand his Home Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,8,Fhave faced growing criticism on their
OL,9,Fwider immigration agenda - including
OL,10,Ffrom their own backbenchers.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, Angela Rayner hit out at
OL,13,FMahmood's plans to double the time it
OL,14,Ftakes for most migrant workers to
OL,15,Fqualify for permanent residence from
OL,16,Ffive years to 10 years - calling them
OL,17,F'un-British' and a 'breach of trust'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
