PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774026671
OL,3,CUK border chief to step down after
OL,4,Cfailure to reduce small boat crossings
OL,6,FThere have also been reports that
OL,7,FLabour MPs against the plans are
OL,8,Fthreatening to force a vote in
OL,9,FParliament on the reforms if ministers
OL,10,Fdon't change tact.
OL,12,FCommenting on the announcement, a home
OL,13,Foffice spokesperson thanked Hewitt for
OL,14,Fhis "dedicated leadership".
OL,16,F"We would like to thank Martin Hewitt
OL,17,FCBE QPM for his dedicated leadership
OL,18,Fsince the creation of the Border
OL,19,FSecurity Command.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
