OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774026671
OL,3,CUK border chief to step down after
OL,4,Cfailure to reduce small boat crossings
OL,6,F"Over the past 18 months, the Border
OL,7,FSecurity Command has brought
OL,8,Fgovernment agencies, law enforcement
OL,9,Fand international partners together to
OL,10,Ftackle people smuggling gangs, as well
OL,11,Fas seeing the Border Security, Asylum
OL,12,Fand Immigration Act into law."
OL,14,FITV News understands that interim
OL,15,Farrangements are being made before a
OL,16,Fsuccessor is announced.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
